root
  html tag="script"
  line_break
  line_break
  html tag="Hero" self_closing=true
  line_break
  line_break
  html tag="div" class="comicSans"
    line_break
    html tag="p"
      paragraph
        text "Did you enjoy your lunch, mom? You drank it fast enough. I know, I just call her Annabelle cause she's shaped like a…she's the belle of the ball"
        text "! YOU'RE the Chiclet"
        text "! Not me. Caw ca caw, caw ca caw, caw ca caw"
        text "! A Colombian cartel that WON'T kidnap and kill you. You go buy a tape recorder and record yourself for a whole day. "
        html tag="a" class="link" href="https://bluthipsum.com/"
          text "I think you'll be surprised at some of your phrasing."
    line_break